import { Component } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-nav', templateUrl: './nav.component.html', styleUrls: ['./nav.component.css'] }) export class NavComponent { isMenuOpen: boolean = false; isSubMenuOpen: boolean = false; isAdminVisible: boolean = false; checkAdminVisibility() { this.isAdminVisible = true; } toggleMenu() { this.isMenuOpen = !this.isMenuOpen; this.isSubMenuOpen = false; } toggleSubMenu() { this.isSubMenuOpen = !this.isSubMenuOpen; } }
